s inflated its population data so much that its status as the world&rsquo;s most populous country may be false<br />\n    This happens so provinces can get education subsidies and Beijing can hide the results of decades of family planning<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3018829/chinas-population-numbers-are-almost-certainly-inflated-hide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fcomment%2Fopinion%2Farticle%2F3018829%2Fchinas-population-numbers-are-almost-certainly-inflated-hide&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=64cbea5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3018829/chinas-population-numbers-are-almost-certainly-inflated-hide</a>"},{"pid":"1d8872bccc1798864e965e30524f69c820f2f08a","tid":1641460,"uid":136640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57916c6dacdb28e7742e5ed1b16528588bee689e","tid":1641460,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f61fdfcb80b82f5a893702db33d54acd89c5181d","tid":1641460,"uid":174498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:43:26.000Z","msg":"如果係造假 較大機會係報細數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 方便刷人均gdp"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:47:58.000Z","msg":"呢家人均GDP好好咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:14:15.000Z","msg":"其實已經報細左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}